<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="277">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$meng-ban-yu-sheng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/meng-ban-yu-sheng" class="zg-link" title="梦伴余生">梦伴余生</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wu-zhen-ming-64" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wu-zhen-ming-64" class="zg-link" title="吴臻鸣">吴臻鸣</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xue-guan-yang" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xue-guan-yang" class="zg-link" title="薛冠扬">薛冠扬</a></span>
