<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2565578" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/6f4e096edb38fed86cb41a8bf35ba523_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="540" data-rawheight="450" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="540" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/6f4e096edb38fed86cb41a8bf35ba523_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="540" data-rawheight="450" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="540" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/6f4e096edb38fed86cb41a8bf35ba523_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/6f4e096edb38fed86cb41a8bf35ba523_b.jpg"><br>萨菲罗斯的发型如果投影到二维平面上就是个角，同时也表现了为什么角会变方向。<br>大概是这样的发型让人看起来比较能打，就像有些发型让人看起来有钱或是像领导。


</div>

